description: In Guernsey's general election, voters will have 38 votes to assign between about 100 candidates.
title: Guernsey's 2020 election 'will be the strangest in the world'
title_page: Guernsey's 2020 election 'will be the strangest in the world' - BBC News
maintext: "I think I will read a little bit of the manifestos and skim read it, but there are certain people that I will not be voting for this time, and others I want to keep in," she added.
